               <head>Savanih-i ahval-i Ashob</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Savāniḥ-i ʿumrī-yi Āshūb by Mīrzā Muḥammad Bakhsh "Āshūb" ibn Muḥammad Ghiyās̲</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85010050 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008115920" n="1" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_4034-item1">
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="person_f5798">Mīrzā Muḥammad Bakhsh "Āshūb" ibn Muḥammad Ghiyās̲</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="per" key="person_f5798" type="supplied">ميرزا محمّد بخش آشوب ابن محمّد غياث</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21960">Savāniḥ-i ʿumrī-yi Āshūb</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_21960">سوانح عمرى آشوب</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Alternatively known by the title: Sharḥ-i aḥvāl-i Āshūb</p>
                        <p>Alternative title stated on title page (f. 1r): Savāniḥ-i ʿumrī-yi Mirzā Muḥammad Bakhsh mutakhalluṣ bah Āshūb va khānadān-i ū</p>
                        <p>Brief autobiography, generally lacking chronological details</p>
                        <p>Supplementary account of the author's ancestors follows autobiography</p>
                        <p>Lacking addition account of Ashob's elder brother, Muẓaffar Ḥusayn 'Ḥusayn'</p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per" xml:lang="per">Persian</textLang>
                     <note>Transcribed by order of <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f7663" role="fmo">G. J. Nicholls</persName>, Judge at <name type="place">Farrukhabad</name>, from a manuscript obtained from <name type="place">Agra</name>
